<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA522_05_IH_0001_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema522_05.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema522_05_ih_0001">
      <section class="title type2 score">
        <h2 data-head="1" lang="y" class="fraction_box_title">
          <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
            <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
              <span lang="y">그림을 보고</span>
              <div class="operation_box">
                <span>4</span>
                <span>×</span>
                <div class="mixed_fraction">
                  <span>1</span>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>1</span>
                    <span>5</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <span lang="y">을 두 가지 방법으로 계산하려고 합니다.</span>
              <span class="empty_box nemo"></span><span lang="y">안에 알맞은 수를 써넣으세요.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </h2>
      </section>
      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <div class="dashed_line_box">
            <dt lang="y" class="label_method">방법1</dt>
          </div>
          <div class="question_box justify_center dir_col">
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA522_05_IH/0001_03.png" alt="" />
              <ul class="text_number1">
                <li>0</li>
                <li>4</li>
              </ul>
              <ul class="text_number2">
                <li>0</li>
                <li>1</li>
                <li>2</li>
                <li>3</li>
                <li>4</li>
              </ul>
              <div class="text1">4 × 1</div>
              <div class="text2">
                4×
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>1</span>
                  <span>5</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="input_area flex align_center gap_10 mt_36 bracket">
              <span>4 × 1</span>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>1</span>
                <span>5</span>
              </div>
              <span>= (4 × 1) +</span>
              <span class="bracket-l"></span>
              <span>4 ×</span>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="1" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>

                <span>5</span>
              </div>
              <span class="bracket-r"></span>
              <span>= 4+</span>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="4" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="5" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
              </div>
              <span>=</span>
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="4" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
              </div>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="4" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div> </span
                ><span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="5" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- 해설 -->
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p>
                    <span lang="y">대분수를 자연수와 진분수의 합으로 나타내어 계산했습니다.</span>
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <div class="dashed_line_box">
            <dt lang="y" class="label_method">방법2</dt>
          </div>
          <div class="question_box justify_center dir_col">
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA522_05_IH/0001_04.png" alt="" />
              <ul class="text_number3">
                <li>0</li>
                <li>1</li>
                <li>2</li>
                <li>3</li>
                <li>4</li>
                <li>5</li>
              </ul>
              <div class="text3">
                4×
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>1</span>
                  <span>5</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="text4">
                4×
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>6</span>
                  <span>5</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="input_area flex align_center gap_10 mt_40">
              <span>4 × 1</span>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>1</span>
                <span>5</span>
              </div>
              <span>= 4 ×</span>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="6" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>

                <span>5</span>
              </div>
              <span>=</span>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>
                  4 ×
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="6" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
                <span>5</span>
              </div>
              <span>=</span>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span
                  ><div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="24" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field></div></span
                ><span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="5" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
              </div>
              <span>=</span>
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="4" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
              </div>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="4" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div> </span
                ><span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="5" text-align="center" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- 해설 -->
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p>대분수를 가분수로 나타내어 계산했습니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
